Date Reviewed: 09/05/07 lenodell Member Since: 23/04/07
View Member's: Reviews Orders despatched quickly and correctly. Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 02/11/06 Moslin Member Since: 16/10/06
View Member's: Reviews Stock availability was a bit hit and miss as the phrase 'Regularly stocked item' does not mean a lot. I would have liked to have bought everything from Ballicom but oddly there is a hole in the product range with no AM2 heatsinks or matched DDR2 memory kits. Their pricing is very competetive and their customer service and delivery time of this, my first order, was spot on. I would certainly use them again based on my last experience. Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 20/10/06 neilperrins Member Since: 11/10/06
View Member's: Reviews Need to have the shipping costs up front. When you offer a "free" delivery service over £100, you shouldn't charge £3+ for delivery, should you? Whoops! Oh, and no VAT invoice - i had to ask for one. Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 20/09/06 paul Member Since: 11/09/06
View Member's: Reviews low shipping charge was a pleasant surprise; little info offered on my wanted product but I had already researched it; the barclaycard payment pages were clunky and obscured my address, otherwise the site was fine Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 20/09/06 atanas Member Since: 11/09/06
View Member's: Reviews I made couple of purchases from ballicom.co.uk They have very good prices in the market. Also their delivery is fast. I highly recommend this seller. Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 01/06/06 MSmith1970 Member Since: 20/05/06
View Member's: Reviews Keyboard ordered Saturday. Quoted delivery 5 days. Emailed them at 7 days. Told keyboard out of stock! Ballicom HAD MY MONEY FOR A WEEK! Told 2 weeks to be back in stock + 5 days to send it me! Nice way to profit on my £64. Told them reimburse me as I was disgusted by this. Seems that these days companies are only in it for the money not to give the people what they want. I would never use Balicom again! Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 11/05/06 kelmenzies Member Since: 11/05/06
View Member's: Reviews Ordering was very easy, communication from Ballicom was excellent and the item arrived next morning. Thank you very much. I would definitely recommend you! Overall Rating

View Member's: Reviews You PopUp menu COVERED the order number!! Stupid or what? Overall Rating

View Member's: Reviews I haven't received the goods yet - so final summary not able to be given. but it was a quick and pleasureable experience none the less Overall Rating

View Member's: Reviews Shopper Survey box appeared on screen as soon as order was placed and covered the confirming message which contained my order number! Difficult to uncover this and fill in number on survey. I did not see any notification re delivery time. Overall Rating
